The great migrations
Romania is not and will not be prepared for what is to come.
What about Europe?
I say it from the beginning, clearly and bluntly: the 7,000 refugees that Romania should and must naturalize is, in itself, an insignificant number, but huge compared to the capacity of the Romanian state to manage such a project .
